流速。\n排雷：\n双标签俩角，，签约改标签，非，著包配哈。\n谢穷，痛屏蔽，宝宝避雷哈。','',0,'','fanqie',0,0,3,'2026-06-18 17:52:04','2026-06-19 02:49:46','https://p3-reading-sign.fqnovelpic.com/novel-pic/p2o85449042a2087e0e91a6aafb0e78830d~tplv-resize:225:0.image?lk3s=5b7047ff&x-expires=1782379331&x-signature=532HLUAgo2UIqxd%2BgJOWZL13hbs%3D','covers/fanqie/fanqie_7466117635466333209.image'),('7468317647302560793','猛，撕厉鬼！','红芝麻','https://fanqienovel.com/page/7468317647302560793','【玄➕沙雕微恐➕抓鬼➕灵异➕算➕爽】\n\n    林丢二找，观。\n\n    ，搭喜脉。\n\n    二，掐指算，李婆戴绿帽，。\n\n    ，司，浇财树，拳献祭程序，且五楼跳毫伤。\n\n    ，掐指算，苏千肚宝贝婿野。\n\n    乱乱，乱套。\n\n    京城佬跪求算。\n\n    众掌权状，砚珩脸足蛋糕林，斩钉截铁造谣。\n\n    林松松厉鬼拳灰飞湮灭。\n\n    砚珩:猛，婆撕厉鬼！\n\n    怎办，急，线。','',0,'','fanqie',0,0,3,'2026-06-18 17:52:04','2026-06-19 02:49:47','https://p3-reading-sign.fqnovelpic.com/novel-pic/p2o6d70eb5bee7571d7ab922d4bcd934159~tplv-resize:225:0.image?lk3s=5b7047ff&x-expires=1782379347&x-signature=Zb7NvWVBsxYjCmSosBi35z11774%3D','covers/fanqie/fanqie_7468317647302560793.image'),('7468327768753720344','野救队，线肘击','若辞','https://fanqienovel.com/page/7468327768753720344','【+群+末灾+市脑洞，则八，合则灭危】\n队线务，拯救\n隐藏，肘击\n准则：肘，灾祸永慢步！\n：谢夏队送肘击礼包，拒收退哈。\n域灾祸：希夏队整，祸祸！\n夜语毕业，，找班。\n二，司炸，末推\n夜语：怪咯？\n夏层聚集队陷沉思，队伍，脏。\n：谢谢，，建议散。\n冰冷榜，绝骄\n热二，提陌刀砍，智商线超绝猛汉\n阳朗，际热闹嫌\n喜欢甜食，添嘴毒绝犟\n技术黑客，倒霉闻悲催\n怂吐槽，端局夜语\n队爆，线肘击，，线拯救','',0,'','fanqie',0,0,3,'2026-06-18 17:52:04','2026-06-19 02:49:47','https://p3-reading-sign.fqnovelpic.com/novel-pic/p2o4925793d819d07235e831d76c21d8acd~tplv-resize:225:0.image?lk3s=5b7047ff&x-expires=1782379324&x-signature=JiA7PZPwQTro75EATfYqbuR9r8s%3D','covers/fanqie/fanqie_7468327768753720344.image'),('7469963068374518808','鸦仙','封卷','https://fanqienovel.com/page/7469963068374518808','寒夜鸦鸣，踏仙途。\n韩榆蜷缩破院角落，奄奄息。\n乌鸦落肩——\n“娃交宝贝，爷领。”黑袍嘶哑，韩榆交祖传修仙，掌悄复刻二枚。\n，修仙铁律：\n摸，！\n——\n《靠复制修仙薅羊毛件》《修仙养乌鸦！》《杂役超强谨慎》','',0,'','fanqie',0,0,3,'2026-06-18 17:52:04','2026-06-19 02:49:48','https://p3-reading-sign.fqnovelpic.com/novel-pic/p2oa9a3ee44b0d84401e5aeeda99c776848~tplv-resize:225:0.image?lk3s=5b7047ff&x-expires=1782379324&x-signature=ufTzqxP569QZt8Vdi5mqaDRP2bg%3D','covers/fanqie/fanqie_7469963068374518808.image'),('7470142203893926936','怎敌','彼呦','https://fanqienovel.com/page/7470142203893926936','【签版】\n【校园+救赎+暗恋+双洁】\n媚嗲精  偏执隐忍\n*\n，霁青清冷，显赫耀贵，靠改寒奇迹，狼狈嫁，苏夏八辈修。\n苏夏，霁青疯。\n喜欢湿沉，喜欢掌控欲，怕双苍形。\n霁青保护。\n百亿遗产，苏夏始眠，惊醒，梦霁青“夏夏”，鲜血浸透俊脸。\n*\n睁，二。\n苏夏庭，众星捧。\n霁青刚转校临，旧球鞋刷洗泛，眉冷淡。\n苦，偏执。\n愿桌，攥紧裙摆，椅，鼓勇。\n亡，辈。\n，\n缠哦。\n*\n:\n.，双洁；\n.；\n.雌竞，慢慢改，始疯；\n.“亡哥”容，+亡哥专番，线雪故归始，集束，请务必错','',0,'','fanqie',0,0,3,'2026-06-18 17:52:04','2026-06-19 02:49:48','https://p3-reading-sign.fqnovelpic.com/novel-pic/p2o46fe0879e8f16a6916031dc243621f51~tplv-resize:225:0.image?lk3s=5b7047ff&x-expires=1782379346&x-signature=qOd9pnZFhefQnnnD6ZYuVW0mOvo%3D','covers/fanqie/fanqie_7470142203893926936.image'),('7470466292764380222','京澳春潮','仲夏雨','https://fanqienovel.com/page/7470466292764380222','【签】\n【姐九流】《京澳春潮》\n温凝澳岛谢屿，危险。即混迹糖铺，静静碗绿豆沙。\n窄店铺，鼎沸，敢拼桌。圆米，刻隔绝片孤岛。\n“谁？”\n“谢屿。澳岛敢惹，——啊喂，哪？”\n温凝弯眉：“识啊。”\n***\n澳岛京城，。\n谢屿誓辈踏片，订婚赶抓。\n“？”\n隔薄薄片板，未婚。温凝透紧。\n“？”谢屿徐徐摩挲指枚素戒，眸暗沉，“戴送戒指，嫁谁？”','',0,'','fanqie',0,0,3,'2026-06-18 17:52:04','2026-06-19 02:49:49','https://p3-reading-sign.fqnovelpic.com/novel-pic/p2o0f21e1a4f0dc85a4e4e787c0e1405cea~tplv-resize:225:0.image?lk3s=5b7047ff&x-expires=1782379348&x-signature=Y6f%2F27T1qeulHcyn6mrpOrGqjtI%3D','covers/fanqie/fanqie_7470466292764380222.image'),('7471175817268055102','架空古：江南营致富','汀雨','https://fanqienovel.com/page/7471175817268055102','[古营致富]+[江南]+[短]+[松甜爽]\n松压，盛江南户营，温馨欢喜，仁义，讲述古普百姓，角王侯，勋爵豪。\n伊始，笔桃源，盛，百姓居，底层众努存，营富贵，遇，苦鲜，妇户。\n　　历史千众故拼集，故。','',0,'','fanqie',0,0,3,'2026-06-18 17:52:04','2026-06-19 02:49:49','https://p3-reading-sign.fqnovelpic.com/novel-pic/p2ofbdeeefc88d7c7887210836852adb2ae~tplv-resize:225:0.image?lk3s=5b7047ff&x-expires=1782379341&x-signature=MdRqB9j8zUqFVnONNQQp%2BQ4QNyc%3D','covers/fanqie/fanqie_7471175817268055102.image'),('7471211401080491033','：局击杀夏禾，邪','孟良柒','https://fanqienovel.com/page/7471211401080491033','【，系统，搞松，敌，，杀伐断，邪，洗夏禾...】\n玄霄穿越，幼惨，侥幸龙虎，灵玉哥...\n传弟，丧仇恨，玄霄誓杀...\n:“，错，饶吧。”\n玄霄:“错，！”\n夏禾:“，该？”\n玄霄:“？妖速速！”\n哪:“投降，玄霄收吧！”\n玄霄:“，辈！”\n...\n玄霄除魔卫，醒义系统，义获奖励...\n邪府弟。\n:“哪啊，！”','',0,'','fanqie',0,0,3,'2026-06-18 17:52:04','2026-06-19 02:49:49','https://p3-reading-sign.fqnovelpic.com/novel-pic/p2o47494db849a38d8f071967ab46f472e4~tplv-resize:225:0.image?lk3s=5b7047ff&x-expires=1782379336&x-signature=cjeAlpsufj1wmWUa%2Fhu3Da7vbXU%3D','covers/fanqie/fanqie_7471211401080491033.image'),('7471658055080348697','留守北荒','程狗','https://fanqienovel.com/page/7471658055080348697','红旗陷害，差投倒判刑，贵助。\n背，即移送青站，遣返城。\n红旗临选择，背城，瞧，连累。\n，北荒落户，彻底弃青份。','',0,'','fanqie',0,0,3,'2026-06-18 17:52:04','2026-06-19 02:49:50','https://p3-reading-sign.fqnovelpic.com/novel-pic/p2o155ca205894677ecdf4f05b8d7de912e~tplv-resize:225:0.image?lk3s=5b7047ff&x-expires=1782379329&x-signature=nWt4cWyfRLg9%2B90XaBtbgFVBvHk%3D','covers/fanqie/fanqie_7471658055080348697.image'),('7476824735003724825','幕映：震撼古！','枯木浮','https://fanqienovel.com/page/7476824735003724825','圆夜亮拍照片刘斌祝福，睛空连，切投射古。\n视线，古近史波澜壮阔、跌宕伏，楼厦，百姓丰衣足食，武器强盛势挡……\n纷纷陷震撼痴迷。\n。\n秦始皇：“九揽，五洋捉鳖……华夏竟恐怖！？”\n税收。\n李：“增值税，税，奢侈品税，税收针富呀，社义吗？”\n粮食产量。\n朱元璋：“杂交稻，亩产斤！！！养啊！”\n交展。\n汉武帝：“铁、飞、火！假？”\n建筑制造。\n杜甫：“楼厦，莫非‘广厦千，庇寒俱欢颜’吗？”','',0,'','fanqie',0,0,3,'2026-06-18 17:52:04','2026-06-19 02:49:51','https://p3-reading-sign.fqnovelpic.com/novel-pic/p2ob4a61e6933702269512af36bb4092522~tplv-resize:225:0.image?lk3s=5b7047ff&x-expires=1782379330&x-signature=njbMqFLeOphbMeIGMIIZskn2YKg%3D','covers/fanqie/fanqie_7476824735003724825.image'),('7477576232578599998','哈哈哈，大明','微微的薇','https://fanqienovel.com/page/7477576232578599998','利可共而不可独，独利则败；谋可寡而不可众，众谋则泄。','历史古代',3114137,'连载','fanqie',0,900,3,'2026-06-18 19:10:56','2026-06-19 02:49:51','https://p3-novel-sign.byteimg.com/novel-pic/e7c3b94a0b4c31ed65bd3d1b3a9cc850~tplv-resize:225:300.image?lk3s=191c1ecc&x-expires=1781867456&x-signature=nEoeoWx3z%2Baf7V2d62Zq7adIEyI%3D',''),('7477901455727283225','漫画预言杀人事件','红摇','https://fanqienovel.com/page/7477901455727283225','笔尖野火不灭，书写浮生百态。围脖🍠作者红摇','女频悬疑',393660,'完结','fanqie',0,190,3,'2026-06-18 19:28:53','2026-06-19 02:49:52','https://p9-novel-sign.byteimg.com/novel-pic/p2o38ef49af0b1bf53616c5aef7f3974eff~tplv-resize:225:300.image?lk3s=191c1ecc&x-expires=1781868532&x-signature=p14Hxt9igrlE0CCFUvVIi%2FOAq4A%3D',''),('7478769464138288153','末世文恶毒女配？嚣张一日是一日','云挽财财','https://fanqienovel.com/page/7478769464138288153','祝各位人生海海，尽兴开怀。','科幻末世',1532131,'完结','fanqie',0,732,3,'2026-06-18 19:28:55','2026-06-19 02:49:52','https://p3-novel-sign.byteimg.com/novel-pic/p2obe8297d2a1652941bced3881db7b1bae~tplv-resize:225:300.image?lk3s=191c1ecc&x-ex